ound, {{Span|null}} is returned.=== intersects_segment ===*  [[Vector3 GD|Vector3]] '''intersects_segment''' '''(''' [[Vector3 GD|Vector3]] begin, [[Vector3 GD|Vector3]] end ''')'''Returns the intersection point of a segment from position {{Span|begin}} to position {{Span|end}} with this plane. If no intersection is found, {{Span|null}} is returned.=== is_equal_approx ===*  bool '''is_equal_approx''' '''(''' [[Plane GD|Plane]] plane ''')'''Returns {{Span|true}} if this plane and {{Span|plane}} are approximately equal, by running [[@GDScript GD#is_equal_approx|@GDScript.is_equal_approx()]] on each component.=== is_point_over ===*  bool '''is_point_over''' '''(''' [[Vector3 GD|Vector3]] point ''')'''Returns {{Span|true}} if {{Span|point}} is located above the plane.=== normalized ===*  [[Plane GD|Plane]] '''normalized ( )'''Returns a copy of the plane, normalized.=== project ===*  [[Vector3 GD|Vector3]] '''project''' '''(''' [[Vector3 GD|Vector3]] point ''')'''Returns the orthogonal projection of point {{Span|p}} into a point in the plane.